Install and Uninstall Apps...
helm install <name> <chart location>  # Install the chart with a name
helm install nginx .
 helm uninstall <name>


Perform App Upgrade and Rollback
helm upgrade <name> <chart location>  # Upgrade a release
helm upgrade nginx .
helm rollback <release> <revision>  # Roll back a release to a specific revision


List, Add, Remove, and Update Repositories
helm repo add <URL>  #To add url to repo
helm list     #To list the helms 


Helm Release monitoring

Download Release Information